《'''優涅讀者'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Utne Reader'''''}}，簡稱：{{lang|en|'''''Utne'''''}}）是一家[[美國|美國]]雙月刊雜誌。該雜誌從[[另類媒體|另類媒體]]收集并重新出版關於政治、文化和環境相關文章，這些媒體包括期刊、新聞報紙、電子雜誌、音樂和[[DVD|DVD]]。

== 歷史==

《優涅讀者》由埃里克·優涅（Eric Utne）和妮娜·羅斯柴爾德·優涅（Nina Rothschild Utne）創立於1984年，埃里克主持該雜誌直到1990年代，之後則有妮娜接手。<ref name="Groening">{{cite news |first=Tom |last=Groening |title=Utne CEO, editor recounts magazine struggles |url=http://www.bangornews.com/news/t/midcoast.aspx?articleid=140537&zoneid=179 |work=Bangor Daily News |date=2006-09-16 |accessdate=2007-12-17 }} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>

2003年，《優涅讀者》的封面上加上了副標題“一種不一般的閱讀人生”（A Different Read on Life），其名稱則一度改為只寫Utne。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.magazine-agent.com-sub.info/utne/covers?c=1&cov=COVER0018375.JPG&pg=1 |title=Magazine Agent: ''Utne'' |access-date=2008-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721192843/http://www.magazine-agent.com-sub.info/utne/covers?c=1&cov=COVER0018375.JPG&pg=1 |archive-date=2011-07-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2006年，該雜誌被[[奧格登出版集團|奧格登出版集團]]收購。<ref>{{cite press release  |title=Ogden Publications Acquires Utne Magazine  |date=2006-06-02  |url=http://www.utne.com/magazine/press/20060605.html  |accessdate=2007-12-17  |deadurl=yes  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928035705/http://www.utne.com/magazine/press/20060605.html  |archivedate=2007-09-28  |df=  }}</ref> 也因此名稱改回Utne Reader，不過其任務依然是專注於最初的目標——“最好的另類媒體”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.minnesotamonitor.com/showDiary.do?diaryId=1188 |title=Minnesota Monitor:: Utne Re-Reader: A 'Progressive Brand' Reclaims its Roots - and Name |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927033113/http://www.minnesotamonitor.com/showDiary.do?diaryId=1188 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》認為《優涅讀者》是1980年代美國[[沙龍_(聚會)|沙龍運動]]的組成部份，專注於辯論當時的社會問題。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CE2DB1038F930A25757C0A964958260|title=An Attempted Comeback for the Literary Salon|first=Jonathan|last=Rabinovitz|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1992-04-13|accessdate=2008-03-25}}</ref> 它出現在1990年代的{{link-en|神話傳說男性運動|mythopoetic men's movement}}中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.utne.com/web_special/web_specials_archives/articles/648-1.html |title=The Virtuous Male |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2007-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928035637/http://www.utne.com/web_special/web_specials_archives/articles/648-1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 優涅獨立媒體獎 ==

優涅讀者負責出版“優涅獨立媒體獎”（Utne Independent Press Awards），<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.utne.com/uipa/ |title=Utne Independent Press Awards |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2008-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010154435/http://utne.com/uipa |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該獎頒發給世界各地的另類媒體和獨立媒體。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.utne.com/utne-independent-press-awards-winners-2010.aspx |title=Winners of the 2010 Utne Independent Press Awards |access-date=2013-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66u1N1QMq?url=http://www.utne.com/utne-independent-press-awards-winners-2010.aspx |archive-date=2012-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

